ith transparency, this blouse incorporates sheer panels for a look that is both modest and alluring. Perfect for evening transitions.','EcoVero™ Viscose','both','6500.00','Blouses',0,3,'4.25',4,4,'2024-12-21 14:15:56','2025-12-03 06:37:42'),(118,103,'Embroidered Peasant Blouse','Hand-stitched details adorn the neckline of this peasant-style blouse. The relaxed fit allows for movement while maintaining a polished appearance.','Organic Cotton','handmade','5600.00','Blouses',1,1,'4.75',4,4,'2025-03-22 14:15:56','2025-12-01 16:18:52'),(119,104,'Structured Collar Shirt','A crisp, white shirt reimagined with an exaggerated collar. This piece brings high-fashion drama to a classic wardrobe staple.','Organic Cotton','biodegradable','6200.00','Blouses',0,0,'4.50',4,4,'2024-12-01 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:13:46'),(120,100,'Velocity Performance Top','Engineered for movement, this top wicks moisture while feeling soft against the skin. The streamlined design minimizes friction during intense activity.','Recycled Polyester','both','3500.00','activewear',1,2,'4.25',4,4,'2024-12-21 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:02:52'),(121,101,'Gaia Sport Bra','High support meets high fashion. Featuring a cross-back design and sustainable materials, this sports bra is designed for the eco-conscious athlete.','Recycled Nylon','both','2800.00','Active Wear',1,0,'4.75',4,4,'2025-04-23 14:15:56','2025-12-01 16:18:52'),(122,102,'Core Control Tank','This tank offers gentle compression to support your core during workouts. The minimalist design allows it to double as casual streetwear.','Bamboo Fabric','biodegradable','2200.00','Active Wear',0,0,'4.25',4,4,'2024-11-19 14:15:56','2025-12-03 06:46:47'),(123,103,'Sprint Windbreaker','Lightweight and water-resistant, this windbreaker is crafted from upcycled plastics. It features reflective details for safety during evening runs.','Recycled Plastics','both','5500.00','Active Wear',1,0,'4.75',4,4,'2025-02-26 14:15:56','2025-12-01 16:18:52'),(124,104,'Flow Crop','D