at adds drama to your morning routine. Features wide sleeves and a detachable belt.','Tencel™ Lyocell','both','6500.00','Sleepwear',0,1,'4.50',4,4,'2025-01-30 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:13:26'),(140,100,'Velare Blazer','Tailored to perfection, this blazer features a nipped waist and strong shoulders. A powerful addition to any professional wardrobe.','Organic Wool','biodegradable','12500.00','Jackets',0,1,'4.75',4,4,'2024-11-02 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:02:41'),(141,101,'Gaia Bomber','A sustainable take on the classic bomber jacket. Made from recycled fabrics, it features ribbed cuffs and a zip front.','Recycled Polyester','both','8500.00','Jackets',1,1,'4.25',4,4,'2025-01-09 14:15:56','2025-12-01 16:18:52'),(142,102,'Seta Denim Jacket','Crafted from organic cotton denim, this jacket features unique stitching details and branded hardware. A timeless casual piece.','Organic Cotton','biodegradable','7200.00','Jackets',0,0,'4.75',4,4,'2024-12-20 14:15:56','2025-12-03 06:38:20'),(143,103,'Utility Field Jacket','Functional and stylish, this jacket offers multiple pockets and a drawstring waist. Made from durable hemp fibers.','Hemp Fiber','biodegradable','9500.00','Jackets',1,0,'4.50',4,4,'2024-12-02 14:15:56','2025-12-01 16:18:52'),(144,104,'Vegan Leather Moto','Edgy and cruelty-free. This moto jacket features asymmetrical zips and quilted details, crafted from high-quality pineapple leather.','Piñatex','both','14500.00','jackets',1,1,'4.50',4,4,'2024-11-21 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:20:24'),(145,100,'The trench','A classic trench coat with modern updates. Water-resistant and breathable, it features a double-breasted front and belted waist.','Recycled Polyester','both','15500.00','Coats',0,0,'4.75',4,4,'2024-12-07 14:15:56','2025-12-03 08:00:41'),(146,101,'Gaia Wool Coat','An oversized wool coat that feels like a warm embrace. The dropped shoulders and wide lapels create a relaxed luxury look.','Organic Wool','biodegradable','18000.00','Coats',1,0,'4.25',4,4,'2025-01-12 14:1